reviewText: My daughters (ages 10 and 7) and my son (age 4) all love this movie! I actually had to remove it from the DVD player in the car because after the kids watching it 20 times in a row I was ready for something new! Somehow it made it back in the car a few days later. The music is very cute and the storyline sends a good message.
Great movie! And chorus music is fabulous!!! My 8 yr ol daughter loved it!! I enjoyed this dvd alot! Great value!!!
Bought this item for my granddaughter as she had the shoes and is thrilled with them. She enjoys watching her shoes in the movie!
I didn't watch much of the movie, but my gals 7 & 4 love the movie. My 7 yr old wrote that this was her favorite movie.
My 4 year old loves this movie. She watches it repeatedly and she love her twinkle toe sneakers even more. Definitely recommend to those with little girls. ! !
We rented this video about overcoming bulling and having courage from the library and my daughter was excited to watch it again and again.
My Granddaughter loves it!  She now wants the Twinkle Toe shoes as well which she will get for her Christmas!
my 5 year old loves it. we rented it once from the red box but could not find it in stores.
My 3 year old loves this video. She watches it repeatedly. Definitely recommend to those with little girls. ! !
I bought this for my Grand Daughter for Christmas. She loves it!! Quick shipping. Perfect for her age group 10 years old.

My daughter loved it,

My daughter is just now 5 and I often worry about her finding her own way.  There is so much pressure on kids to fit in that bullying has become an issue.  This movie tells the kids that they can be their own person and that it is not okay to bully or be bullied.  She loves it too.  The dancing, music, and characters jeep her entertained.
Arrived in great condition and before specified time. We have watched this so many times we know the characters part before it is said.

My little niece loves twinkle toes movie! I also bought her twinkle toe shoes! She loves to wear them all the time.
Thanks!
Patricia
Twinkle Toes, Nice story line for kids. We had to purchase the movie because it's one of the movies that your kids will watch over and over.
First came the schoes, then the movie...both are huge hits with our daughter, and our son pretends not to watch the movie...
My 3-year old loves this movie.  She's watched it at least a hundred times and knows the words to it.
My daughter love this movie and the quality of the movie was great thank!!!! I would get more movie from this company
My 3 year old daughter loves it! And there's a good lesson about overcoming your fears...an hour of peace for me..win win
What can I say? This was a gift for a child. It arrived on time and in good condition. I expect she liked it.
It seem like it took a while to come but when it finally arrived my daughter loved it she watches just about everyday.
A cute storyline but overly pushing the cool sparkly shoes.  Six-year old daughter watched once and hasn't wanted to see it again.  This would have been a better Netflix.
It's a cute story that little girls will like but it's also a shameless marketing ploy by Skechers to advertise their $50+ shoes for girls who will likely outgrow them in less than a year.
My daugher loves this movie. I think it is kind of corney but kids like it. I would recommend this movie.
Came omg great without any damages! Came in as promised for delivery
My GD loves twinkle toe sneakers, so the movie was a cherry on top.
My niece watches this movie all the time. She loves it. She has her friends come over to watch it to. Excellent
Got this to go with her shoes!
The movie started out with commercials, which was kind of weird. but had the movie that my granddaughter wanted. In good shape and timely arrival.
Was sent quickly and arrived safely.
